snippet.textDisplay: In fact, the result of this video is a demonstration, not a reality.  Probably they obtained quite similar results between the waters because the containers already have bacteria and fungi.  In addition the air already presents microorganisms naturally.  If they want to show a more reliable result, I suggest sterilizing the containers with 70% alcohol and opening the agar plates just beside a blue flame. Not yet the ideal procedure, but the result will be much more faithful!
